          huc illuc miserum, nec adhuc fortuna satolla est!--
   280    Sic cridat, et fido Sinibaldo cuncta palesat,
          dumque palesat agit centum de fronte colores,
          unde trahit rappas Sinibaldi fazza stupentis,
